OL,3,CTrump wishes Burnham 'good luck' and
OL,4,Cpledges US help in upbeat endorsement
OL,6,FDonald Trump has said Andy Burnham
OL,7,F"has got a big job ahead of him, but
OL,8,Fhe will be able to do it" and pledged
OL,9,Fthat the US "will be there to help".
OL,11,FIn an upbeat message on his Truth
OL,12,FSocial platform, the president also
OL,13,Fwished the new Prime Minister "good
OL,14,Fluck and godspeed".
OL,16,FThe early endorsement of the former
OL,17,FGreater Manchester mayor by the
OL,18,FAmerican leader comes after the pair
OL,19,Fspoke on the phone within an hour of
OL,20,Fthe Makerfield MP arriving in Downing
OL,21,FStreet.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@YO]qD@MOUqD@cO]uD@_OUvD@RO]
