OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784607479
OL,3,CTrump wishes Burnham 'good luck' and
OL,4,Cpledges US help in upbeat endorsement
OL,6,FIt will also assuage fears after the
OL,7,FRepublican president previously
OL,8,Fdescribed Mr Burnham as "extremely
OL,9,Fliberal" and "mayor of a town".
OL,11,FIn addition it signals a fresh start
OL,12,Fin the transatlantic partnership after
OL,13,Frelations with Sir Keir Starmer grew
OL,14,Fincreasingly fractious over the Iran
OL,15,Fwar.
OL,17,FMr Burnham was buoyed in Mr Trump's
OL,18,Feyes after reports he could back new
OL,19,Foil and gas drilling in the North Sea,
OL,20,Fwhich the president has championed.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@HO]qD@NOUqD@^O]
