OL,3,CTrump wishes Burnham 'good luck' and
OL,4,Cpledges US help in upbeat endorsement
OL,6,FMr Trump said at the weekend said
OL,7,Fpeople in Aberdeen would be "dancing
OL,8,Fin the streets" at such a move, albeit
OL,9,Funconfirmed.
OL,11,FThe president, a vocal supporter of
OL,12,Ffossil fuels, insisted further
OL,13,Fdrilling in the North Sea would "make
OL,14,Fthe United Kingdom, from a Poverty
OL,15,FStricken Disaster, to one of the
OL,16,FRichest Countries anywhere in the
OL,17,FWorld".
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@OO]uD@aOUyD@FO]
