OL,3,CTrump wishes Burnham 'good luck' and
OL,4,Cpledges US help in upbeat endorsement
OL,6,FIn his Truth Social Post, Mr Trump
OL,7,Fsaid: "I had a very good conversation
OL,8,Fwith the new Prime Minister of the
OL,9,FUnited Kingdom, Andy Burnham.
OL,11,F"We discussed many subjects, including
OL,12,Fthe outstanding relationship we have
OL,13,Fhad with the UK.
OL,15,F"We will be meeting in the not too
OL,16,Fdistant future for topics of mutual
OL,17,Finterest."
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUwD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
