PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784607479
OL,3,CTrump wishes Burnham 'good luck' and
OL,4,Cpledges US help in upbeat endorsement
OL,6,FHe added: "The Prime Minister has got
OL,7,Fa big job ahead of him, but he will be
OL,8,Fable to do it and, of course, the USA
OL,9,Fwill be there to help!
OL,11,F"We discussed North Sea Oil, Trade,
OL,12,Fthe Military Alliance, Demining of the
OL,13,FHormuz Strait, and many other topics.
OL,15,F"The call was interesting, and went
OL,16,Fvery well. I wished Prime Minister
OL,17,FBurnham, GOOD LUCK AND GODSPEED!"
OL,19,FThe importance of the call had earlier
OL,20,Fbeen hailed by the British embassy in
OL,21,FWashington.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUwD@AOUyD@aO]
