OL,3,CTrump wishes Burnham 'good luck' and
OL,4,Cpledges US help in upbeat endorsement
OL,6,FIn a post on X, the diplomatic mission
OL,7,Fsaid: "Within an hour of taking
OL,8,Foffice, Prime Minister Andy Burnham...
OL,9,Fspoke with President Donald Trump,
OL,10,Funderscoring the importance of the UK/
OL,11,FUS partnership from day one.
OL,13,F"The leaders discussed shared
OL,14,Fpriorities and agreed to remain in
OL,15,Fclose contact."
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOUwD@OO]
